description.en:
What is the project about?
A meme coin on Stonks, its a tribute to the biggest crypto meme ever.  Stonks always go up.

What makes your project unique?
Stonks is one of the most famous crypto meme ever. It is launched by Zeus.eth one of the famous influencer

History of your project.
Launched 15 hours ago with $10 Mil volume. 2000+ holders and more to come. 

What’s next for your project?
Exchange listing and utility announcement

What can your token be used for?
Rewards, staking, utility, and more.
